I have put up for ebay a cab carpet set this includes cab mat, kickpanels, wheel arch carpet and the central seat section, I only used the cab mat and is in good condition with a couple of dirty marks nothing that a good wash would clean up its charcoal grey with dark blue edging all the rest of the carpet never got fitted and has not been cut out for the seat runners or the fuse board cut out in the kick panel.

Have a look its worth a punt.

eBay item number:

291563589844

Happy Days.
